## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely Cause |
|---------|-------------|
| Tool not found | Tool not in `SLACK_MCP_ENABLED_TOOLS` â€” only 6 tools are enabled |
| Channel not found | Wrong ID format or user not a member â€” run `channels_list` with `channel_types` to verify |
| Attachment download fails | File > 5MB or file_id format wrong (must be `Fxxxxxxxxxx`) |
| MCP server not responding | Check `opencode.jsonc` â€” `slack` MCP must be configured and not disabled |
